# Implementation Plan - Smart Reminder System

The goal is to implement a high-frequency, non-annoying reminder system that adapts to user engagement and rotates prompts to prevent fatigue.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> The system relies on `flutter_local_notifications` for local scheduling.
> Logic is deterministic based on the last 7 days of journal history.

## Proposed Changes

### Data Layer

#### [MODIFY] [store.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/services/store.dart)
-   Add `int get entriesInLast7Days` getter to calculate engagement.

#### [NEW] [prompt_library.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/data/prompt_library.dart)
-   Create a static class `PromptLibrary` containing:
    -   `static const List<String> prompts`: 30+ varied, low-pressure prompts.

### Service Layer

#### [MODIFY] [notification_service.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/services/notification_service.dart)
-   **Dependencies**: Integrate with `SharedPreferences` to track:
    -   `last_reminder_schedule_date` (to avoid rescheduling too often).
    -   `recent_prompt_indices` (list of ints) for rotation history.
    -   `reminder_option` (enum: Smart, Daily, Off).
-   **New Method**: `scheduleSmartReminders(int weeklyCount)`
    -   **Logic**:
        -   Count 5-7: Schedule 4-5 times/week.
        -   Count 2-4: Schedule 5-6 times/week.
        -   Count 0-1: Schedule 3-4 times/week.
    -   **Timing**: Random between 7:00 PM and 10:00 PM.
    -   **Content**: Pick from `PromptLibrary`, ensuring no repeats from `recent_prompt_indices`.

#### [MODIFY] [settings_screen.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/settings_screen.dart)
-   Update "Daily Reminders" toggle to a "Notification Mode" selector or keep it simple with "Smart Reminders" toggle.
-   Add options: "Smart (Recommended)", "Daily", "Off".

#### [MODIFY] [main.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/main.dart)
-   Call `scheduleSmartReminders` on app startup (if enabled), passing the current [Store](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/services/store.dart#11-315) count.

